{"tid":1993083,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港地，男人要柒真心難","createTime":"2020-04-28T13:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T07:57:32.000Z","uid":37458,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4003e0fac729e495bfbef021cef810f3c82c3f44","tid":1993083,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"出邊個post講咩高分女拖件低分男<br />\n我眼見啲情侶通常都係條仔正過條女<br />\n香港啲仔外形都係倒模咁襯衫，再gel個頭，戴隻入門撈<br />\n係咁意，執下個樣，花少少錢去建身，花時間同錢、心機；我真係未見過有仔係柒。<br />\n仲要依家啲仔會做下運動，後生啲既仲有d係基。<br />\n相反啲女，講真有幾多係識襯衫？個樣靚女？一般都中年發福，只會越嚟越肥，一個唔好彩，甩頭髮就柒上加柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其與花咁多時間係度叫春，不如執靚女自己算啦。"},{"pid":"8dc9648d7f8dd072a240c1af727a050c9e6510e2","tid":1993083,"uid":231583,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/221057_4a99d5ca65fc075006c818bca7837ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F221057_4a99d5ca65fc075006c818bca7837ec9.jpg&h=71c013b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0608e89d570f25a183052d843a2d60f0b75dea8","tid":1993083,"uid":20586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:49:33.000Z","msg":"未見過中大迷你龍？"},{"pid":"de4b3ac395df286411458041ee76b832aca56e3e","tid":1993083,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:50:05.000Z","msg":"連登仔mode：其實唔難<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb38c1549d2103656dea12a9cd8303a5293bd2c7","tid":1993083,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8dc9648d7f8dd072a240c1af727a050c9e6510e2","tid":1993083,"uid":231583,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/221057_4a99d5ca65fc075006c818bca7837ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F221057_4a99d5ca65fc075006c818bca7837ec9.jpg&h=71c013b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/221057_4a99d5ca65fc075006c818bca7837ec9.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"16f962e218c87005956159cda84c6a7e4152c122","tid":1993083,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0608e89d570f25a183052d843a2d60f0b75dea8","tid":1993083,"uid":20586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:49:33.000Z","msg":"未見過中大迷你龍？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"人地有拎套"},{"pid":"cd324c60057b7d12136c8723fb4373bf958e290e","tid":1993083,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"咪撚搞咁多野，剩係襯黑同白，個頭唔好油，個人乾淨D都夠你食女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a526d5b2d98fb8f7bb5407bb10b6a70b43ac656","tid":1993083,"uid":48195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"下出街啲男十個有九個都係倒模式但又好撚柒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著champion咩Fila果啲柒袋加一模一樣既頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲女有化妝(喬裝)依樣野真係唔會柒得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非唔打扮既肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普遍女都貪靚點都會畫個眉搽下base查下唇膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297142738efe3139387d64bb3995471b9c3739d1","tid":1993083,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"笑撚左，抄我個POST，都好心用下腦先啦<br />\n香港D男仔外形俾人笑左咁多年<br />\n你仲話要柒真心難<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40254d94355992cc44a2ff6f34f0ca0f326e9084"